  <div class="role">
    <h3><a href="https://www.w3.org/">W3C</a> (January 2024 - Present)</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Invited Expert - Accessibility Guidelines Working Group</strong>
    </p>
    <p>
      Around my work at Octopus, I joined the Accessibility Guidelines Working
      Group at W3C as an invited expert. My role involves helping to build the
      next version of WCAG, so that it's easier than ever for people across the
      web to make their websites more accessible.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can
      <a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/GL"
        >read more about what we're working on here</a
      >.
    </p>
